@hostname = localhost:3000

### Get all transfers
GET http://{{hostname}}/api/transfers
Content-Type: application/json

### Create new transfer
POST http://{{hostname}}/api/transfers
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 5,
    "sourceId": 1,
    "targetId": 2
}

### Create new transfer (Error, wrong target ID)
POST http://{{hostname}}/api/transfers
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 5,
    "sourceId": 1,
    "targetId": 99
}